</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Bamboo Grove" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Sun pokes through the bamboo trees in Arashiyama. 嵐山の竹林の間から朝日が差し込む。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2505_A7R04509-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2505_A7R04509-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Osaka Central Public Hall・大阪市中央公会堂</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250523/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Osaka Central Public Hall・大阪市中央公会堂" /><published>2025-05-23T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-05-23T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/osaka-hall</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250523/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
