</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Osaka" /><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Built in 1918, this Osaka landmark has been a public venue since its inception, hosting operas, concerts, lectures, and other art and cultural events. 1918年に建てられたこの大阪のランドマークは、開館当初から公共の場として、オペラ、コンサート、講演会、その他の芸術・文化イベントを開催してきた。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2505_DSC_0320_ai_ai-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2505_DSC_0320_ai_ai-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Evening Primrose・月見草</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250522/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Evening Primrose・月見草" /><published>2025-05-22T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-05-22T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/primrose</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250522/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
