</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Flowers" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[There was beautiful late afternoon light on these pink Evening Primrose flowers, so I stopped to take a few shots. このピンクの月見草の花には午後の終わりの美しい光が当たっていたので、立ち止まって何枚か写真を撮った。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2505_A7R04454.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2505_A7R04454.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Wild Nature・自然</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250520/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Wild Nature・自然" /><published>2025-05-20T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-05-20T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kamogawa</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250520/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
