鴨川沿いの石垣の隙間から生えている花。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Kamo River" /><category term="Foliage" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[WIldflowers growing out of a space in the stone wall, along the Kamogawa river. 鴨川沿いの石垣の隙間から生えている花。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2505_DSC_0277_ai.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2505_DSC_0277_ai.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Peaceful Morning・平和な朝</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250519/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Peaceful Morning・平和な朝" /><published>2025-05-19T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-05-19T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/oigawa</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250519/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
